flowchart LR
    CHANGE[Engineering Change] --> AI[AI inspects code and context]
    AI --> FINDINGS[Ranked findings, summaries, and suggestions]
    FINDINGS --> HUMAN[Human validates and decides]
    HUMAN --> APPLY[Apply or modify]
    HUMAN --> REJECT[Reject or defer]
    HUMAN --> INVESTIGATE[Investigate independently]
    APPLY --> OUTCOME[Changed artifact and downstream outcome]
    REJECT --> OUTCOME
    INVESTIGATE --> OUTCOME

    AI -. potential offload .-> HUMAN
    FINDINGS -. possible cognitive reload .-> HUMAN
    OUTCOME --> EVAL[Measure effort, quality, latency, and learning]
